交集选择器：
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <style>
        .rich {
            color:gold;
        }
        .beauty {
            color: red;
        }
        /* p元素且类名为beauty */
        p.beauty {
            color:aqua;
        }
        .rich.beauty {
            color:orange;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h2 class="rich">土豪张三</h2>
    <h2 class="beauty">明星李四</h2>
    <h2 class="rich beauty">土豪明星王五</h2>
    <br>
    <p class="beauty">小狗旺财</p>
    <p class="beauty">小猪佩奇</p>
</body>
</html>
